    "UIName": "Pixie",
    "Id": "chassisdef_pixie_PX-FS",
    "Name": "Pixie",
    "Details": "The PX-FS is the forestry kit, built around a four-ton Buzzsaw in the right arm as its primary tool. A Clan-sourced Flamer in the left arm clears underbrush and unusable materials. The Clan-made Flamer was specifically chosen to save on weight within the tight fifteen-ton budget. Full environmental sealing is standard.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.97</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_stilettostardrive"
  },
